description: The first two trays of the Pfizer/BioNTech vaccine, enough for 975 people, arrived on Wednesday.
title: Island coronavirus vaccinations could start on Monday
title_page: Island coronavirus vaccinations could start on Monday - BBC News
maintext: The first phase of the rollout is expected to last eight weeks with people receiving the vaccination during this first stage in nursing homes, healthcare facilities or one of the island's two hospitals.
